history.content: CS 61c is a lot of work, way more than 1B. In 61c there are projects basically every week on top of hws and labs and keeping up with the somewhat difficult material. In math 1B, you just have hws and keeping up with somewhat high school level material. So, it is fair to say that 61c is much much more work than math 1b.
